   answer:"A（3π）",
   sol:"①弧长=60/360×2π×9=3π；②选A（3π）",error:"弧长=（圆心角/360°）×2πR",
   svg:`<svg width="200" height="180" viewBox="0 0 200 180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="background:#0d1825;border-radius:8px;display:block">
