  {id:461,yr:2017,city:"宁夏",type:"choice",topic:"arc_area",score:3,diff:2,
   subTopics:["arc_area","pythagorean"],methods:["m20"],
   content:"圆锥底面半径r=3，高h=4，则圆锥的侧面积为（）A.12π B.15π C.24π D.30π",
