  <text x="45" y="85" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">PA=?</text>
</svg>`},
    {id:"b_cir_04",diff:2,content:"PA、PB是⊙O两切线，PA=6，PB=？",answer:"6",sol:"切线长定理",error:"同一点两切线等长",upLink:["tg08","tg09"],downLink:[]},
    {id:"b_cir_05",diff:2,content:"内接四边形ABCD，∠A=80°，∠C=？",answer:"100°",sol:"对角互补",error:"圆内接四边形对角互补",upLink:["tg08","tg09"],downLink:[],
     svg:`<svg width="200" height="195" viewBox="0 0 200 195" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="background:#0d1825;border-radius:8px;display:block">
